name: The Little Million @ The Boardwalk, Sheffield. Single Release Party!!!
description:
To celebrate the release of their debut single, You and Me Against The Universe, The Little Million will be playing at The Boardwalk in Sheffield on Monday 15th March. Support comes from Laruso and Friends of Heroes.

£4.00 per ticket and 16+ are welcome.

PLEASE NOTE - WE MAY NOT BE ABLE TO SEND TICKETS OUT IN TIME. IF THAT IS THE CASE, YOUR NAME WILL BE LEFT ON THE DOOR.

GIG DETAILS
Monday 15th March
Doors at 7pm - 10pm
Tickets £4.00
16+ Welcome
Support: Laruso and Friends of Heroes
